♪ I would give a lamb ♪

1179
01:10:06,737 --> 01:10:11,509
♪ If I were a wise man ♪

1180
01:10:11,544 --> 01:10:16,251
♪ I would do my part ♪

1181
01:10:16,287 --> 01:10:21,320
♪ Yet what I can I give him ♪

1182
